            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a boiler flue gas desulfurization and carbon dioxide resource utilization system and method. The system comprises a boiler flue, a flue gas booster fan, a flue gas washing device, a carbon dioxide absorption device, a water supplementing device, a sediment treatment device and a sulfurous acid pump. The boiler flue is a flue after denitration and dust removal of a boiler, an outlet of the boiler flue is connected to an inlet of the flue gas booster fan, an outlet of the flue gas booster fan is connected to a first inlet of the flue gas washing device, an outlet of the water supplementing device is connected to a second inlet of the flue gas washing device, and a first outlet of the flue gas washing device is connected to a first inlet of the carbon dioxide absorbing device. A second outlet of the flue gas washing device is connected to an inlet of the sulfurous acid pump, and a third outlet of the flue gas washing device is connected to an inlet of the sediment treatment device. According to the method, the pollution waste gas sulfur dioxide in the boiler flue gas is subjected to resource utilization, an industrial product sulfuric acid is generated, and clean energy hydrogen is generated; and carbon emission and the like are not additionally generated in the sulfur dioxide removal process."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种锅炉烟气脱硫及二氧化碳资源化利用的系统和方法，该系统包括锅炉烟道、烟气增压风机、烟气洗涤装置、二氧化碳吸收装置、补水装置、沉渣处理装置和亚硫酸泵；锅炉烟道为锅炉脱硝、除尘后的烟道，其出口接至烟气增压风机的入口，烟气增压风机的出口接在烟气洗涤装置的第一入口，补水装置的出口接在烟气洗涤装置的第二入口，烟气洗涤装置的第一出口接在二氧化碳吸收装置的第一入口，烟气洗涤装置的第二出口接在亚硫酸泵的入口，烟气洗涤装置的第三出口接在沉渣处理装置的入口。该方法将锅炉烟气中的污染性废气二氧化硫资源化利用，产生了工业产品硫酸，产生了清洁能源氢气；在进行二氧化硫脱除过程中没有额外产生碳排放等。"
                }
            ]
